zhao.algorithmMagic.integrator

接口 AlgorithmIntegrator<AlgorithmType>

  • 类型参数:
    AlgorithmType - 算法实现类型
    所有已知实现类:
    HashClassificationIntegrator, ImageRenderingIntegrator, IncrementalLearning, Route2DDrawingIntegrator

    public interface AlgorithmIntegrator<AlgorithmType>
    算法集成器,是针对每一个算法的实际应用模块,这里有着针对算法的调用逻辑封装,您不需要去自己实现算法的应用.

    The algorithm integrator is the actual application module for each algorithm. There is a logical encapsulation of the calling logic for the algorithm, and you do not need to implement the application of the algorithm yourself.

        Run the integrator and return the result of the operation. The function is run with parameters. When the operation is successful, it will return a double type parameter.
